vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.loading.window

Interface ILoadingWindowStatus


  • public interface ILoadingWindowStatus
    The main status to be shown on the LoadingWindow during startup. Updated using BandWagon.playEvent(vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.universal.band_wagon.Event), playing a LoadingManager.UpdateStatusEvent.

    GenElectrovise
